==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|-}}

# A theory, as proposed by [[w:Leon Trotsky|Leon Trotsky]], that a people can be led to [[communism]] by an educated minority. This is in opposition to standard communist theory which calls for the understanding of the majority.

